?id=V70CAAAAYAAJ&amp;pg=PA172\"><i>The Deserted Bride: And Other Poems</i></a>. New York: D. Appleton. pp.&#160;87\u201388, 172.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Deserted+Bride%3A+And+Other+Poems&amp;rft.place=New+York&amp;rft.pages=87-88%2C+172&amp;rft.pub=D.+Appleton&amp;rft.date=1843&amp;rft.aulast=Morris&amp;rft.aufirst=George+Pope&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DV70CAAAAYAAJ%26pg%3DPA172&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ASally+St.+Clair\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation book\">Wildwood, Warren (1866). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://books.google.com/books?id=215aAAAAYAAJ&amp;pg=PA78\">\"The Romance of War.&#8212;Sergeant Jasper and Sally St. Clair\"</a>. <i>Thrilling Adventures Among the Early Settlers</i>. Philadelphia: J. Edwin Potter. pp.&#160;78\u201381.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.atitle=The+Romance+of+War.%26mdash%3BSergeant+Jasper+and+Sally+St.+Clair&amp;rft.btitle=Thrilling+Adventures+Among+the+Early+Settlers&amp;rft.place=Philadelphia&amp;rft.pages=78-81&amp;rft.pub=J.+Edwin+Potter&amp;rft.date=1866&amp;rft.aulast=Wildwood&amp;rft.aufirst=Warren&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3D215aAAAAYAAJ%26pg%3DPA78&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ASally+St.+Clair\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<table class=\"metadata plainlinks stub\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"background:transparent\"><tbody><tr><td><a href=\"/wiki/File:Gentileschi,_Artemisia_-_Clio_-_1632.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Stub icon\" src=\"//upload